                "invention-title": [
                    "Electrothermal catalytic ammonia synthesis denitration system",
                    "一种电热催化合成氨脱硝系统"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention provides an electro-thermal catalytic ammonia synthesis denitration system. The system comprises a compression unit, a synthesis tower, a catalyst layer, a power supply unit, a mixer, a pressure reduction unit and an SCR (Selective Catalytic Reduction) reactor, the input end of the compression unit is connected with a first nitrogen conveying pipe and a hydrogen conveying pipe; the compression unit is used for compressing nitrogen and hydrogen; the bottom of the synthesis tower is connected with the output end of the compression unit; at least one catalyst layer is fixed in the synthesis tower; the power supply unit is positioned outside the synthesis tower, is connected with the catalyst layer and supplies power to the catalyst layer; the first input end of the mixer is connected with the output end of the synthesis tower, and the second input end of the mixer is connected with a second nitrogen conveying pipe; the output end of the mixer is connected with the pressure reduction unit, and the output end of the pressure reduction unit is connected with the SCR reactor, the flue gas denitration process of the coal-fired power plant can be shortened, and the flue gas denitration device is economical, feasible, low in pressure, safe and low in carbon emission."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明提供一种电热催化合成氨脱硝系统，包括压缩单元、合成塔、催化剂层、供电单元、混合器、减压单元和SCR反应器；所述压缩单元的输入端连接有第一氮气输送管和氢气输送管；所述压缩单元用于对氮气和氢气进行压缩；所述合成塔的底部与所述压缩单元的输出端连接；所述合成塔的内部固定有至少一层催化剂层；所述供电单元位于所述合成塔的外部，并与所述催化剂层连接，为催化剂层供电；所述混合器的第一输入端与所述合成塔的输出端连接，第二输入端与第二氮气输送管连接；所述混合器的输出端与所述减压单元连接，所述减压单元的输出端与所述SCR反应器连接，本发明能够缩短燃煤电厂烟气脱硝流程，不仅经济可行、低压安全，且碳排放少。"
                }
            ]
